<subSubSection id="C33329B6049E15CDFFB44DF8FDFAFBC7" pageId="151" pageNumber="152" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B967A3D049E15CDFFB44DF8FDFAFBC7" blockId="151.[151,1436,802,1075]" pageId="151" pageNumber="152">
<emphasis id="B95DA62F049E15CDFFB44DF8FEE0FC1F" bold="true" box="[151,267,977,1003]" pageId="151" pageNumber="152">Remarks.</emphasis>
The genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C2901BE049E15CDFEB64DFBFDF5FC1F" authorityName="Finlay" authorityYear="1926" box="[405,542,978,1003]" class="Gastropoda" family="Triphoridae" genus="Notosinister" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ptenoglossa" pageId="151" pageNumber="152" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B95DA62F049E15CDFEB64DFBFDF5FC1F" box="[405,542,978,1003]" italics="true" pageId="151" pageNumber="152">Notosinister</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is of masculine gender, therefore the original spelling should be 
<taxonomicName id="4C2901BE049E15CDFA304DFBFF1DFBFB" authorityName="Laseron" authorityYear="1954" class="Gastropoda" family="Triphoridae" genus="Notosinister" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ptenoglossa" pageId="151" pageNumber="152" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="robustus">
<emphasis id="B95DA62F049E15CDFA304DFBFF1DFBFB" italics="true" pageId="151" pageNumber="152">Notosinister robustus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<typeStatus id="5492C49F049E15CDFE264DDFFE9EFBE4" box="[261,373,1014,1040]" pageId="151" pageNumber="152">Lectotype</typeStatus>
designation by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC049E15CDFD094DDCFD0FFBFB" author="Marshall, B. A." box="[554,740,1013,1039]" pageId="151" pageNumber="152" pagination="1 - 119" refId="ref160499" refString="Marshall, B. A. (1983) A revision of the recent Triphoridae of southern Australia. Records of the Australian Museum, Supplement 2, 1 - 119. https: // doi. org / 10.3853 / j. 0812 - 7387.2.1983.102" type="journal article" year="1983">Marshall (1983)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC049E15CDFDCC4DDCFC4EFBFB" author="Marshall, B. A." box="[751,933,1013,1039]" pageId="151" pageNumber="152" pagination="1 - 119" refId="ref160499" refString="Marshall, B. A. (1983) A revision of the recent Triphoridae of southern Australia. Records of the Australian Museum, Supplement 2, 1 - 119. https: // doi. org / 10.3853 / j. 0812 - 7387.2.1983.102" type="journal article" year="1983">Marshall (1983)</bibRefCitation>
considered this species a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C2901BE049E15CDFFB44A30FDE7FBC7" authority="Hedley, 1903" authorityName="Hedley" authorityYear="1903" box="[151,524,1049,1075]" class="Gastropoda" family="Triphoridae" genus="Triphora" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Asparagales" pageId="151" pageNumber="152" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="maculosa">
<emphasis id="B95DA62F049E15CDFFB44A30FE86FBC7" box="[151,365,1049,1075]" italics="true" pageId="151" pageNumber="152">Triphora maculosa</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC049E15CDFE574A30FDE7FBC7" author="Hedley, C." box="[372,524,1049,1075]" pageId="151" pageNumber="152" pagination="596 - 619" refId="ref154294" refString="Hedley, C. (1903) Studies on Australian Mollusca. Part. 7. Proceedings of the Linnean Society of New South Wales, 27, 596 - 619." type="journal article" year="1903">Hedley, 1903</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
